group as compared with the non-resected group. However, considering the 
postoperative length of life, palliative gastrectomy seems applicable to cases 
of P1, H1, partly to H2, n3(+), and S3, but in more advanced cases, it was 
learned essential to determine the surgical method in consideration of the 
nature of the cancer in the individual cases.

